data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhome with attached garage! This townhome is in a great location outside the hustle and bustle of city living, yet minutes away from I-15, restaurants, shopping, golf courses, parks and more. Large spacious kitchen that has been tastefully updated. Fresh new paint  throughout and other upgrades listed under the documents tab. Storage room under stairs and built in overhead storage racks in the garage are an added bonus.
